longBusinessSummary: Dala Energi AB (publ) operates as a supplier of electricity, heating, and fiber networks in Sweden. It operates an electricity grid; and produces and distributes district heating to industrial properties, multi-family buildings, administration premises, schools, and single-family homes in Leksand and Insjön. The company was incorporated in 1897 and is based in Leksand, Sweden.
